@@ -0,0 +1,439 @@
+/*
+ * IR SIR driver, (C) 2000 Milan Pikula <www@fornax.sk>
+ *
+ * sir_ir - Device driver for use with SIR (serial infra red)
+ * mode of IrDA on many notebooks.
